      "id": "structured",
      "name": "Structured with Examples",
      "prompt": "Analyze this photo for home inventory.\n\nReturn JSON with:\n- room: string (kitchen, bedroom, garage, etc.)\n- area: string or null (where in room)\n- container: string or null (drawer, shelf, bin, etc.)\n- items: array of {name: string, attributes?: object}\n\nExample output:\n{\"room\": \"kitchen\", \"area\": \"counter\", \"container\": null, \"items\": [{\"name\": \"toaster\"}, {\"name\": \"knife block\"}]}"
    },
    {
      "id": "finding-focused",
      "name": "Finding-Focused",
      "prompt": "You're helping someone find things in their home later. For this photo:\n1. What room is this?\n2. Where exactly in the room?\n3. Is there a container (drawer, box, shelf)?\n4. List every findable item using common search terms.\n\nBe specific about location. Use names people would search for."
    }
